node_5.subject: carlos gomez
node_5.description: This is carlos gomez's plan for Friday March 07: Wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am., Have breakfast at 8:00 am., Read and write poetry in his home office at 9:00 am., Take a walk in the park to clear his mind at 11:00 am., Have lunch at 12:00 pm., Work on poetry submissions and research on AI economy articles at 1:00 pm., Take a short break with coffee at 3:00 pm., Leave for the Gardner family's house for the family gathering at 3:45 pm., Attend a family gathering at the Gardner family's house at 4:00 pm., Attend Carmen's speech in the common room at 4:05 pm., Discuss issues related to the development of the virtual economy with Carmen in the empty guest bedroom and refute her views at 4:10 pm., Conclude the family gathering and head to the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 5:00 pm., Encounter Carmen again and continue the argument at the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 5:30 pm., Leave the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 7:00 pm., Have a light dinner at 7:30 pm., Relax and read a book at 8:00 pm., Reflect on the day's discussions and write a journal entry at 9:00 pm., Prepare for bed at 9:30 pm., Go to bed at 10:00 pm..
